import { IonInput, IonItem, IonLabel } from "@ionic/react"
import { Button, Form, Row } from "react-bootstrap"
import Title from "../../components/Title"
import FormLogin from "../Login/components/FormLogin"

const NuevoUsuario: React.FC = () => { 

    return <>
        <Title name='Nuevo' />
        <Form>
            <Row>
                
            <FormLogin
                title='Nombre(s)'
                required={true}
                minLength={8}
                type='text'
                name='apP'
                placeholder='Nombres...'
                size="sm"
            />
            <FormLogin
                title='Ap. Paterno'
                required={true}
                minLength={8}
                type='text'
                name='apP'
                placeholder='Apeido paterno'
                size="sm"
            />
            <FormLogin
                title='Ap. materno'
                required={true}
                minLength={8}
                type='text'
                name='apM'
                placeholder='Apeido materno '
                size="sm"
            />

            <FormLogin
                title='Correo'
                required={true}
                minLength={8}
                type='email'
                name='user'
                placeholder='usuario@dominio.abc'
                size="sm"
            />
            </Row>
            <Button> GUARDAR</Button>
        </Form>
    </>
} 

export default NuevoUsuario;
